{"type":"message","id":"a1fc217c","parentId":"d0c6b0fc","timestamp":"2026-02-24T20:05:30.257Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:e66b45d2-9e23-460e-9820-43461e9752ec evolver-self-evolution] 执行完整自进化任务（主动改进）：\n\n## Phase 1: 上下文收集\n1. 读取 evolution-store 配置：/root/.openclaw/workspace/.cursor/evolution-store.json\n2. git pull 最新的进化历史\n3. 读取当前的 Skills：/root/.openclaw/workspace/skills/*/SKILL.md\n\n## Phase 2: 深度分析\n1. 分析最近 **12 小时**内的 session transcripts（不要只看 1 小时）\n2. 读取最新的日志分析报告：/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log-analysis-*.md\n3. 识别 **所有** 重复出现的问题（不限制数量）\n4. 分析错误根因和修复机会\n\n## Phase 3: 主动改进（重要）\n每次执行必须完成以下至少一项：\n\n**A. 创建新 Skill**（如果发现重复工作流）\n- 分析哪些操作被重复执行\n- 提炼成可复用的 Skill\n- 保存到：/root/.openclaw/workspace/skills/evolved-*/\n\n**B. 改进现有 Skill**（如果发现效率问题）\n- 识别现有 Skill 的不足\n- 更新 SKILL.md 添加最佳实践\n\n**C. 生成修复脚本**（如果发现可自动修复的问题）\n- 创建修复脚本\n- 保存到：/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/\n\n**D. 更新进化历史**\n- 记录本轮发现和改进\n- 更新 pattern-registry.md\n\n## 输出要求（重要）\n1. **生成进化报告**：/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/evolution-YYYY-MM-DD-HHMM.md\n2. **报告内容**：\n   - 发现的问题列表\n   - 采取的改进措施（A/B/C/D 中哪项）\n   - 创建/修改的文件列表\n   - 预期效果\n3. **如果创建了新 Skill 或脚本**：列出文件路径\n\n## 注意\n- 不要只是说\"无需更新\"然后跳过\n- 主动寻找改进机会\n- 即使系统稳定，也要考虑是否有优化空间\nCurrent time: Wednesday, February 25th, 2026 — 4:05 AM (Asia/Shanghai)"}],"timestamp":1771963530256}}
{"type":"message","id":"b9eddc53","parentId":"a1fc217c","timestamp":"2026-02-24T20:05:45.490Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这是一个 cron 任务，要求我执行完整的自进化任务。让我按照要求的步骤进行：\n\n## Phase 1: 上下文收集\n1. 读取 evolution-store 配置\n2. git pull\n3. 读取 Skills\n\n## Phase 2: 深度分析\n1. 分析最近 12 小时内的 session transcripts\n2. 读取最新的日志分析报告\n3. 识别重复问题\n4. 分析错误根因\n\n## Phase 3: 主动改进\n必须完成至少一项：创建新 Skill / 改进现有 Skill / 生成修复脚本 / 更新进化历史\n\n## 输出\n生成进化报告到 /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/evolution-YYYY-MM-DD-HHMM.md\n\n让我开始执行。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我将执行完整的自进化任务。让我按照三个阶段进行。\n\n## Phase 1: 上下文收集"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_09b14ef020d64b1fb0de0fae","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/.cursor/evolution-store.json"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a73b9466686745f2af5d4b9b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspace && git pull origin main 2>&1 || echo \"Git pull completed or not needed\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6bf0b0106b08427d8278f8bc","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /root/.openclaw/workspace/skills -name \"SKILL.md\" -type f 2>/dev/null | head -20"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":537,"output":278,"cacheRead":10176,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10991,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771963530257}}
