，距上次调整 20.2 分钟\",\"sessionId\":\"f87c4984-391a-42d9-a28c-4b5d107d6e3b\",\"sessionKey\":\"agent:main:cron:760c35f7-a3b5-4944-b2c9-78e13a7a2894:run:f87c4984-391a-42d9-a28c-4b5d107d6e3b\",\"runAtMs\":1771962040738,\"durationMs\":17370,\"nextRunAtMs\":1771962330167,\"model\":\"glm-5\",\"provider\":\"zai\",\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":654,\"output_tokens\":171,\"total_tokens\":90801}}\n{\"ts\":1771962362325,\"jobId\":\"760c35f7-a3b5-4944-b2c9-78e13a7a2894\",\"action\":\"finished\",\"status\":\"ok\",\"summary\":\"**自适应调度器执行报告 (2026-02-25 03:45)**\\n\\n**系统状态**\\n- CPU: 10% | 内存: 71.5% | 磁盘: 77.2%\\n- 负载级别: **低**\\n\\n**结果**: 跳过调整 — 负载未变化，距上次调整 25.0 分钟\",\"sessionId\":\"f87c4984-391a-42d9-a28c-4b5d107d6e3b\",\"sessionKey\":\"agent:main:cron:760c35f7-a3b5-4944-b2c9-78e13a7a2894:run:f87c4984-391a-42d9-a28c-4b5d107d6e3b\",\"runAtMs\":1771962330172,\"durationMs\":32149,\"nextRunAtMs\":1771962630167,\"model\":\"glm-5\",\"provider\":\"zai\",\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":699,\"output_tokens\":142,\"total_tokens\":91204}}\n{\"ts\":1771962651235,\"jobId\":\"760c35f7-a3b5-4944-b2c9-78e13a7a2894\",\"action\":\"finished\",\"status\":\"ok\",\"summary\":\"**自适应调度器执行报告 (2026-02-25 03:50)**\\n\\n**系统状态**\\n- CPU: 4% | 内存: 66.5% | 磁盘: 77.2%\\n- 负载级别: **低** (频率倍数 0.5x)\\n\\n**任务调整结果 (5/5 成功)**\\n\\n| 任务 | 新间隔 |\\n|------|--------|\\n| evolver-log-analysis | 30 分钟 |\\n| evolver-self-evolution | 2 小时 |\\n| evomap-auto-bounty | 10 分钟 |\\n| novel-marketing-research | 3 小时 |\\n| novel-marketing-execute | 34 分钟 |\\n\\n系统负载低，配置已更新，运行正常。\",\"sessionId\":\"f87c4984-391a-42d9-a28c-4b5d107d6e3b\",\"sessionKey\":\"agent:main:cron:760c35f7-a3b5-4944-b2c9-78e13a7a2894:run:f87c4984-391a-42d9-a28c-4b5d107d6e3b\",\"runAtMs\":1771962630173,\"durationMs\":21057,\"nextRunAtMs\":1771962930167,\"model\":\"glm-5\",\"provider\":\"zai\",\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2105,\"output_tokens\":233,\"total_tokens\":91816}}\n{\"ts\":1771962956958,\"jobId\":\"760c35f7-a3b5-4944-b2c9-78e13a7a2894\",\"action\":\"finished\",\"status\":\"ok\",\"summary\":\"**自适应调度器执行报告 (2026-02-25 03:55)**\\n\\n**系统状态**\\n- CPU: 49% | 内存: 69.2% | 磁盘: 77.2%\\n- 负载级别: **低**\\n\\n**结果**: 跳过调整 — 负载未变化，距上次调整 5.0 分钟\",\"sessionId\":\"f87c4984-391a-42d9-a28c-4b5d107d6e3b\",\"sessionKey\":\"agent:main:cron:760c35f7-a3b5-4944-b2c9-78e13a7a2894:run:f87c4984-391a-42d9-a28c-4b5d107d6e3b\",\"runAtMs\":1771962933674,\"durationMs\":23279,\"nextRunAtMs\":1771963230167,\"model\":\"glm-5\",\"provider\":\"zai\",\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":972,\"output_tokens\":157,\"total_tokens\":92300}}","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1771963595869}}
