{"type":"message","id":"e2d81fae","parentId":"8635ac95","timestamp":"2026-02-24T20:08:23.213Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我发现 git remote 配置错误。evolution-store.json 指向 evolver_history.git，但实际的 git remote 是 swe-agent-node.git。这是一个需要修复的问题。\n\n让我继续创建其他改进，然后生成进化报告。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_49cc618671104ddab93da2fb","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspace && git remote set-url origin https://github.com/shinjiyu/evolver_history.git 2>&1 && echo \"✅ Git remote 已更新\" && git remote -v"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8ecf40528dc04001953d02ea","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/skills/meta_skills/skills/skill-mining/SKILL.md","offset":1,"limit":50}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":3130,"output":142,"cacheRead":30336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33608,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771963697157}}
{"type":"message","id":"dd0ec4c8","parentId":"e2d81fae","timestamp":"2026-02-24T20:08:23.226Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_49cc618671104ddab93da2fb","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ Git remote 已更新\norigin\thttps://github.com/shinjiyu/evolver_history.git (fetch)\norigin\thttps://github.com/shinjiyu/evolver_history.git (push)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":10,"aggregated":"✅ Git remote 已更新\norigin\thttps://github.com/shinjiyu/evolver_history.git (fetch)\norigin\thttps://github.com/shinjiyu/evolver_history.git (push)","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1771963703225}}
{"type":"message","id":"00ea3d1f","parentId":"dd0ec4c8","timestamp":"2026-02-24T20:08:23.230Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_8ecf40528dc04001953d02ea","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: skill-mining\ndescription: Skill/Rule 生成的标准流程与质量规范。skill-miner 执行日志模式挖掘、创建 Skill/Rule 时使用。\n---\n\n# Skill 挖掘输出规范\n\n定义从 Agent 执行日志中提炼 Skill/Rule 的标准流程、质量检查清单和协作工作流。\n\n## When to Use\n\n- skill-miner 执行日志模式挖掘任务\n- 需要创建或更新 Skill、Rule、Subagent\n- 输入包含 log-analyzer 分析报告\n- 需要确保输出与现有配置一致、可追溯\n\n---\n\n## 依赖与协作关系\n\n本 Skill **定义标准流程与质量规范**，需要配合以下组件使用：\n\n| 组件 | 路径 | 职责 | 必需 |\n|------|------|------|------|\n| `skill-miner-enhanced` Rule | `cross-evolution/rules/skill-miner-enhanced.md` | 定义**实施增强指引**（置信度标注、抽象层次、一致性检查、引用验证） | 是 |\n| `evolution-history` Skill | `cross-evolution/skills/evolution-history/SKILL.md` | 进化轨迹追踪（项目进化用本地文件，自身进化用 git 仓库） | 是 |\n| `log-analysis` Skill | `cross-evolution/skills/log-analysis/SKILL.md` | 上游输入：归纳 Agent 的标准化分析报告 | 可选 |\n\n### 独立使用时的最小要求\n\n若未加载 `skill-miner-enhanced` Rule，实施时需自行确保：\n- 单日志来源标注 `待多项目验证`，多日志标注 `基于 N 次会话提炼`（Rule §1）\n- 区分**领域特定**（→ Skill）与**可抽象通用**（→ Rule）的边界（Rule §2.2）\n- 创建/更新前检查与已有 Rule/Skill 是否矛盾或重复（Rule §4）\n- 引用现有组件前先搜索确认其存在（Rule §7）\n\n---\n\n## 标准流程\n\n### Phase 0：历史咨询（前置步骤）\n\n**必须**在正式分析前根据进化场景读取历史（详见 `evolution-history` Skill 的双模式设计）：\n\n**项目进化模式**（改进目标项目的 Rule/Skill）：\n1. 检查项目根目录 `evolution-history/` 是否存在\n   - 不存在 → 首轮，跳过，直接进入 Phase 1\n   - 存在 → 读取 `manifest.md` 和 `pattern-registry.md`（热区）\n2. 执行循环检测\n\n\n[183 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1771963703228}}
{"type":"message","id":"af333345","parentId":"00ea3d1f","timestamp":"2026-02-24T20:08:35.320Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我已经修复了 git remote 配置。现在让我更新 skill-mining skill，添加文件操作最佳实践，然后生成进化报告。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_84cdaed845284ac29686c443","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/skills/meta_skills/skills/skill-mining/SKILL.md","oldText":"---\n\n## 标准流程","newText":"---\n\n## 文件操作最佳实践\n\n在创建或修改文件时，遵循以下原则：\n\n### 1. Read 前检查\n\n```bash\n# 在读取文件前，先检查文件是否存在\nif [ -f \"$FILE_PATH\" ]; then\n  # 执行 read 操作\nelse\n  echo \"文件不存在，跳过或创建新文件\"\nfi\n```\n\n### 2. Edit 精确匹配\n\n- 使用 `edit` 工具时，`oldText` 必须**完全匹配**目标文本\n- 注意空白字符（空格、制表符、换行符）\n- 如果不确定，先 `read` 文件获取精确文本\n\n### 3. 批量修改策略\n\n- 对多个文件执行相同操作时，使用循环\n- 每次修改后验证结果\n- 记录修改摘要便于回溯\n\n### 4. 错误恢复\n\n如果 `edit` 失败：\n1. 重新 `read` 文件获取最新内容\n2. 检查是否有并发修改\n3. 使用更精确的匹配文本\n4. 必要时使用 `write` 覆盖整个文件\n\n---\n\n## 标准流程"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d5b20b34c3704d10ac7154bd","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/pattern-registry.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":817,"output":361,"cacheRead":33408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34586,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771963703230}}
