00（97 次）更高，需要特别关注。\n\n---\n\n*报告生成: evolver-log-analysis*\n*✅ Health: 9/10*\n*🔴 New: 10:00 is highest risk hour*\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772037024017}}
